<template>


<BlogPost
  v-for="post in posts"
  :key="post.id"
  :title="post.title"
 />
</template>


<script>
import blog from "../components/testBlog.vue"

export default {
  name :"blog",
  component: {blog},

  data() {
    return {
      posts: [
        { id: 1, title: 'My journey with Vue' },
        { id: 2, title: 'Blogging with Vue' },
        { id: 3, title: 'Why Vue is so fun' }
      ]
    }
  }
}

</script>
